>> What is the derivative of the loss function [mathjaxinline]E = \frac{1}{2} \sum_{i,j} (y_{ij} - \hat{y}_{ij})^2 = \frac{1}{2}L^{(2)} [/mathjaxinline] w.r.t each output? <<

(x) [mathjaxinline] \frac{\partial E}{\partial y_{ij}} = (y_{ij} - \hat{y}_{ij}) [/mathjaxinline] 
( )  [mathjaxinline] \frac{\partial E}{\partial y_{ij}} = \frac{1}{2} (y_{ij} - \hat{y}_{ij}) [/mathjaxinline] {{ There is no ½ for the derivative}}
